\f0\fs28 \cf0 The outliner and corkboard are not only great organisational tools: they can also be used to navigate, just like the binder, using the \'93Selection Affects Other Editor\'94 tool:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\li720\fi-720\sl264\slmult1\sa360\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	1.	}{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "scrivlnk://6DA3324E-530B-4B9B-93EC-763F87C25D00"}}{\fldrslt Split the editor}} if necessary.\
{\listtext	2.	}In the other editor, load any folder and switch to either corkboard or outliner mode.\
\pard\tx720\sl264\slmult1\sa360\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Note the button containing an arrow pointing out of a box in the footer bar:\
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf0 {\*\shppict{\pict {\*\nisusfilename Tutorial-1}\picw40\pich36\picwgoal800\pichgoal720\pngblip }}
